body_html: @aaroey I think in tensorflow Conv2DTranspose operation (i.e. deconvolution) is implemented as Conv2DBackpropInput type, but in TensorRT documentation they mentioned as ConvTranspose2D. I think is should be a documentation error, since I think tensorflow doesn't have ConvTranspose2D type. But they should refer to the same thing.
